main event: Two circular objects were sighted in England on 29 Sep 52, stationary, then moved off at high speed and disappeared into the clouds.
interesting points: The objects were described as circular planes with a diameter of 5 inches., The observation lasted for about 3 minutes., The sighting was made by a person familiar with aircraft flying at the speed of sound., A RAF fighter had reported a target in the area about 10 minutes before the sighting., The objects moved off in a southern direction and exhibited no exhaust.
sighted object: two circular objects in the sky
witness description: a person with experience observing aircraft
